      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just don't see the point anymore. the nerve pain has been so bad for weeks and there is literally nothing the doctors can do. it never stops. i'm just so tired of fighting a body that's constantly attacking me. it feels like i'm just waiting for a break that's never coming.",
